<h5 id="subject_1113885">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=125359.msg1113885#msg1113885" rel="nofollow">Re: 第2章：创造角色【第三部分：基础信息、品德】</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1113885'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1113885'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #3 于:</strong> 2021-05-21, 周五 12:19:42 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1113885_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
